name: Wilsons Creek
description:
A world class canyon consisting of a deep/narrow slot, fun jumps, and crystal clear water.

Approach

Start by hiking up the ramp on the canyon left side of the bridge. Hike a short distance to a split and stay right. Continue on the well tracked trail until you get to the creek crossing. Cross the creek and gain a nice ridge to the canyon right side of the creek. Follow the well tracked ridge down to Wilson.
